title: Senatorial Saviors, Dance Movies All The Same? 8.17.20

description:
In episode 695, Jack and Miles are joined by There Are No Girls On The Internet's Bridget Todd to discuss the Trump administrations war on the USPS, The Chamber of Commerce defending the GOP, Desperados, Work It, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. USPS MAILBOXES REMOVED IN NYC ... As Trump's War Rages On
  2. Tester demands answers from Postmaster General on reports of mailbox removals
  3. Chamber to launch ads defending embattled GOP senators
  4. WATCH: Louis Prince - The Number Thirteen (Official Visualizer)
